Message.message: You have love in your heart, Lass.
So your heart can weather Despair.
And you've others who love you.
The war can't last forever, Lass.
Think of the time we shared.
Then bottle your grief up tight.
I wish I could be there, Lass.
You're loved. You'll find a way.
It may waver, but it stays lit.
Save no Despair for me, Lass.
For I have hope as well.
